FBIS3-20242 "drweu060_j_94007" FBIS-WEU-94-060 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Mar 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Communist Leaders Concede Election Defeat LD2803213894 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext in Italian 2118 GMT 28 Mar 94 LD2803213894 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext Language: Italian Article Type:BFN [Text] "The Progressives have been defeated," Communist Renewal Leader Fausto Bertinotti and its president, Armando Cossutta, said at a news conference after the announcement of the exit polls results. "However, the Progressives fielded a consistent side. The battle for shaping Italian society has still to be fought."
